---
title: Mexican Street Corn with Avocado-Black Bean Salsa and DIY Tortilla Chips
description: Elote is the Mexican-style corn on the cob that's popular in the streets of Mexico! We're pairing our version with a delicious black bean-avocado salsa, with homemade tortilla chips to scoop it up.
